text: Ærest of cranmerc on þone ðorn.
Of ðam ðorne andlang stræt on þonne blacan pyt.
Of ðam blacan pytte on ða stræt, andlang strete on stodfald.
Of ðam stodfalde on þone litlan broc, andlang broces on blacan mere.
Of blacan mere on þæt slæd, andlang slædes on blacan mor.
Of þam more on þet slæd, andlang slædes<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð on eardes treow.
Of þam treowe on ða sealt stræt, andlang þere salt strete on wilmanford.
Of earnes hlewe on Cyneuerðæs pyt.
Of Cyneuerðæs pitte, andlang heafdon on hwitan dic, andlang hwitan dic on ða holan furh.
Of ðære holan furh<../images/tbar.gif>on þene hricweg.
Andlang weges on clæihæma broc, andlang broces<../images/tbar.gif>eft on cranmere.
